file.name: info.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  x-version-api: fragment of version API
paths:
  /info/version:
    get:
      description: Gets information as to what this server is.
      operationId: getInfoVersion
      tags:
        - InfoService
      responses:
        200:
          description: The basic  information on this server
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ApplicationVersionInfo"
components:
  schemas:
    ApplicationVersionInfo:
      type: object
      required:
        - name
        - version
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        version:
          type: string
